40|$|Chances are you’ve heard ads on {{television}} {{telling you to}} check your credit score. But what is a credit score, and why does it matter? A good credit score helps you to get better interest rates on home or car loans. Your credit history can determine whether {{you get a good}} job, a decent apartment or reasonable rates on insurance. Lenders and others use credit scores to determine how likely you are to make payments on time. Building a good credit history is more important than ever. Check your <b>credit</b> <b>report.</b> It’s important to make sure your <b>credit</b> <b>report</b> is accurate. You can order a free <b>credit</b> <b>report</b> annually from each of the major <b>credit</b> <b>reporting</b> agencies. Order online a...|$|R
